########## STRUCTURES ############

### EDIT ATTRIBUTES - PROPERTIES MANUALLY! (e.g. MULTIVALUE, MAXLISTSIZE, ...

### cf. https://www.sketchengine.eu/documentation/corpus-configuration-file-all-features/

STRUCTURE "doc" {
	TYPE "map32"
